{"tid":1378873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發！】明天（29日）「一人出政總靜坐」對打國務院記招！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:12:53.000Z","uid":98477,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b34eac180f216ec86d6c0c1362b992d1295aba7a","tid":1378873,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:55:19.000Z","msg":"【突發！】明天（29日）「一人出政總靜坐」對打國務院記招！<br />\n<br />\n聽日（29日）國務院下午3:00 開記招，會講述香港當前局勢。（新聞原文在最下，自己睇。）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央可以公開講，證明中央同香港已經傾好數點拆呢個《反逃》修例膠局。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而同時係今晚，即係28日，係上環前線手足同警察打咗反修例運動以來最長既一仗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家會覺得聽日（29日）中央會點講？ <br />\n<br />\n但無論中央點講，記住中央唔同港府：<br />\n港府出嚟係廢Up，但中央出得嚟講嘅係係定調！定性！確立立場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果中央要幫呢個個幾月嘅運動定調，我哋聽日都要幫自己嘅運動，重申一次我哋嘅立場、訴求同埋展現支持嘅人數！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呼籲聽日7月29日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一邊記招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋一邊企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係政總靜坐，表達我一直以來堅持嘅聲音！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為，<br />\n我們不要被中央政府就這場運動定調<br />\n我們不要讓港府有機會得到中央撐腰 <br />\n我們要救個多月嚟嘅反逃運動<br />\n我們要救一直以來嘅義士<br />\n我們要救今晚728 係上環打前線嘅手足 <br />\n<br />\n我們要連結返所有「雞蛋派」聲音，仲要晒出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋派姐係所有唔同色調嘅黃絲，所有係今次運動由藍轉黃嘅人，姐係高牆（強權）嘅對立面，我哋！<br />\n<br />\n聽日729<br />\n人人罷工罷市<br />\n「一人出政總靜坐」<br />\n可手持自製標語<br />\n 黑衣為記 <br />\n重申反《反逃》修例運動以來的五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（新聞原文 Link： <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190728/59872458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59872458&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=331f4e0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59872458&h=b14eb9ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190728/59872458</a>)"},{"pid":"8e9e9944d70eeda761c58da01671af3fa64c8099","tid":1378873,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3108a5e9543bf8cccdda160b23ee09c479a8367","tid":1378873,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d69846d5b98f40464831d6268bf80b93de359503","tid":1378873,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"推上天花板"},{"pid":"b92b98f08aae95ffaa600345415db00e701ea257","tid":1378873,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"6d811cba080169b491907b537ec7ed51ec9a379d","tid":1378873,"uid":9847